OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774440171
OL,3,CLiam and Noel seen smiling together in
OL,4,Crare Oasis reunion tour photos
OL,6,FThe publication chronicles the group's
OL,7,Fmonumental world tour, featuring more
OL,8,Fthan 1,000 unseen and candid, behind-
OL,9,Fthe-scenes snapshots of the brothers
OL,10,Fand their global fanbase.
OL,12,FThe photos were captured by
OL,13,Fphotographer Simon Emmett, the man who
OL,14,Falso took the black-and-white portrait
OL,15,Fof the Gallaghers used to announce
OL,16,Ftheir reunion tour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
