OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774440171
OL,3,CLiam and Noel seen smiling together in
OL,4,Crare Oasis reunion tour photos
OL,6,FEmmett said: "When I saw the reaction
OL,7,Fto the photo, it was obvious to me
OL,8,Fthat this wasn't a single event. The
OL,9,Fphotograph was the beginning of
OL,10,Fsomething.
OL,12,F"I felt strongly that this needed to
OL,13,Fbe documented. There was no facade,
OL,14,Fthis was genuine. We watched the crowd
OL,15,Fhaving the time of their lives, but
OL,16,Fthe band and the crew are also having
OL,17,Fequally as good a time.
OL,26,@nD@NOUtD@AOU
