OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774440171
OL,3,CLiam and Noel seen smiling together in
OL,4,Crare Oasis reunion tour photos
OL,6,FJane Ashton, head of music and
OL,7,Fentertainment at Teenage Cancer Trust,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is such a special
OL,9,Ffundraiser for us as Oasis have been
OL,10,Fhuge supporters of the charity for
OL,11,Falmost 25 years, and we're so very
OL,12,Fgrateful to them for choosing us to
OL,13,Freceive the proceeds from the first
OL,14,Fedition, as well as be associated with
OL,15,Fsuch an iconic tour and product."
OL,17,FOasis first performed at the charity's
OL,18,Fannual Royal Albert Hall show in 2002.
OL,19,FThe auction of the Supernova Edition
OL,20,Fwill take place at the Legends Ball at
OL,21,FGrosvenor House on 19 November.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
