OL,3,CLiam and Noel seen smiling together in
OL,4,Crare Oasis reunion tour photos
OL,6,FThe Oasis' reunion tour was announced
OL,7,Fin August 2024, 15 years after their
OL,8,Fdramatic split in 2009, which was
OL,9,Fprompted by a backstage brawl at the
OL,10,FRock en Seine festival.
OL,12,FThe rock band have had eight number
OL,13,Fone singles and albums each in the UK
OL,14,Fchart, with Wonderwall, Champagne
OL,15,FSupernova, and Some Might Say among
OL,16,Ftheir most well-known hits.
OL,18,FListen to the ITV News' entertainment
OL,19,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
